1.12.name: wordpress/i-dump-iphone-to-wordpress-photo-uploader
1.12.description: i-Dump is a great and fast plugin for WordPress blogs to upload images/photos directly from your Windows desktop into your WordPress i-Dump gallery. Once this plugin is installed you can provide a personal username and password or you can use it in internal group purposes. By this it turns your blog into a social photo blog by letting users share their images or photos! Test it out at http:/www.i-dump.info !
